@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_otabnx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((0.99 / (tmp + 0.71 + v1 + 0.21)) * 0.44)
    v1 = (0.61 / (v0 + v2))
    tmp = (wp.abs(v0) - ((v0 + 0.56 + v0 + 0.85) * 0.14))
    v0 = tmp
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.10) / 0.94) + v1)
    tmp = 0.17
    data[tid] = v0
